granting authority within Member State : Société Nationale des Chemins de Fer Belge (SNCB)/Nationale Maatschappij der Belgische Spoorwegen (NMBS);
form of aid : granting of an extension for payment of debts of EUR 63 million; granting of a recoverable advance of EUR 5 million; granting of a credit facility of EUR 15 million; conversion into a capital increase of debts of EUR 63 million and a loan of EUR 15 million; increase in additional capital of EUR 5 million through contribution in kind from TRW shares;
